English | CBR | 81 Pages

Wolverine: Japan's Most Wanted Infinite Comic #1 (of 13)
Publisher:  Marvel
Publication Date:  July 9 2013

Story:  Jason Aaron and Jason Latour
Script:  Jason Latour
Layouts:  Yves Bigerel
Art:  Paco Diaz
Colors:  Marte Gracia and Izrael Silva
Letters:  Cory Petit

Marvel Comics' latest innovative Infinite Comic is here! Wolverine stars in a weekly adventure from the mind of super star writer Jason Aaron (WOLVERINE AND THE X-MEN, THOR) that pits Wolverine against classic villains and a threat unlike any he has ever faced!

Marvel will release a new digital comic every Tuesday for a year, with four different 13-chapter series each spotlighting one of Marvel's biggest characters.

Thanks goes to Nahga for this release.
